in the kitchen where the big bowls are.

11:15.007 --> 11:16.801
Yeah, well, you know what?

11:16.884 --> 11:19.637
I do what I want. I'm an adult.

11:19.720 --> 11:21.806
So you just get to do
whatever the fuck you want?

11:23.182 --> 11:25.059
-Yeah, I do.
-[lighter clicks]

11:27.269 --> 11:30.564
And when you're an adult,
you can, too, but for now,

11:31.023 --> 11:32.066
you are a kid,

11:32.149 --> 11:35.152
and I would try to hold onto that
for as long as you can, honey.

11:35.236 --> 11:37.488
'Cause let me tell you something,
when you get to the other side,

11:37.571 --> 11:40.282
you are gonna have to deal with
some pretty shitty stuff.

11:42.201 --> 11:43.160
Like I haven't?

11:51.210 --> 11:53.295
[cell phone vibrating]

11:55.339 --> 11:56.424
-Hey.
<i>-</i>[Judy] <i>Hey.</i>

11:56.507 --> 11:57.550
What happened?

11:57.633 --> 12:00.386
<i>-It's okay. They haven't found the car.</i>
-Uh-huh.

12:01.512 --> 12:03.514
<i>-But--</i>
-Uh, gotta go. I gotta go.

12:04.348 --> 12:05.850
Hey. Everything all right?

12:07.184 --> 12:08.185
They, uh...

12:10.020 --> 12:11.021
